302
00:20:57,019 --> 00:20:59,660
Was I hallucinating?

303
00:20:59,660 --> 00:21:04,519
So the two of them resolved their issues too?

304
00:21:07,317 --> 00:21:11,317
Friends, let's create a chatroom for everyone present today.

305
00:21:11,317 --> 00:21:12,880
