306
00:21:12,880 --> 00:21:14,039
Sure!

307
00:21:14,039 --> 00:21:16,739
I'll pay the bill. I'll pay the bill.

308
00:21:51,611 --> 00:21:55,240
You...You...

309
00:22:16,440 --> 00:22:18,140
Why?

310
00:22:25,420 --> 00:22:27,398
On the day of the match,

311
00:22:27,400 --> 00:22:30,797
