313
00:22:37,079 --> 00:22:39,659
Didn't you say that you wouldn't get me a present?

314
00:22:39,659 --> 00:22:41,639
Why did you do that?

315
00:22:42,540 --> 00:22:44,858
I didn't play with you.

316
00:22:44,858 --> 00:22:46,679
I didn't think it counted.

317
00:22:50,039 --> 00:22:51,937
Is it because of that?

318
00:22:54,760 --> 00:22:56,460
No.

319
00:22:59,799 --> 00:23:01,643
I'm just wondering

320
00:23:08,281 --> 00:23:11,160
