321
00:23:11,160 --> 00:23:13,219
I saw it accidentally.

322
00:23:15,459 --> 00:23:17,557
You played two rounds,

323
00:23:17,557 --> 00:23:19,557
and won two Penta Kills.

324
00:23:19,559 --> 00:23:22,119
My rank wasn't that low.

325
00:23:23,440 --> 00:23:25,417
I told my teammates,

326
00:23:25,417 --> 00:23:28,219
"Give me the money. I'll carry you."

327
00:23:28,219 --> 00:23:31,718
Someone in the second game asked, "Why should I?"

328
00:23:31,720 --> 00:23:33,300
Then I answered,

329
00:23:33,300 --> 00:23:35,355
"My girlfriend is watching."

330
00:23:35,355 --> 00:23:38,460
"Brother, please do me a favor."

331
00:23:46,600 --> 00:23:49,420
That is not like you.

332
00:23:50,880 --> 00:23:53,241
I'm not like me now too.

333
00:23:58,320 --> 00:24:02,279
Can we stop talking about the game?

334
00:24:03,000 --> 00:24:04,880
Then what should we talk about?

335
00:24:07,480 --> 00:24:11,680
Does it mean that you've said yes?

336
00:24:14,599 --> 00:24:18,160
I remember, at that time, I asked you other questions too.

337
00:24:20,600 --> 00:24:22,238
Yes.

338
00:24:22,240 --> 00:24:24,251
About immigration to Mars.

339
00:24:27,039 --> 00:24:29,000
You have to keep writing.

340
00:24:33,460 --> 00:24:36,200
- Sure. 
 - But, you don't have to stay up late.

341
00:24:36,200 --> 00:24:38,462
I'm not in a hurry.

342
00:24:39,505 --> 00:24:40,905
All right.

343
00:24:43,400 --> 00:24:46,319
The elevator is cramped. We might as well take the stairs.

344
00:24:53,559 --> 00:24:55,519
They're having a date at the fire escape stairs.

345
00:24:55,519 --> 00:24:57,160
I think there's a story behind them.

346
00:24:57,160 --> 00:24:59,538
The guy is so good-looking.

347
00:24:59,538 --> 00:25:00,998
He has a girlfriend.

348
00:25:00,998 --> 00:25:02,640
Look at how thin his girlfriend is.

349
00:25:02,640 --> 00:25:04,438
She must be pretty too.

350
00:25:04,440 --> 00:25:06,858
I'll start my diet plan after the New Year.

351
00:25:06,858 --> 00:25:09,200
Teacher Yu is so handsome.

352
00:25:10,559 --> 00:25:12,357
When I'm with you,

353
00:25:12,359 --> 00:25:15,340
even the fire escape stairs have become a dangerous place.

354
00:25:15,340 --> 00:25:17,680
Then you have to get used to it as soon as possible.

355
00:25:17,680 --> 00:25:19,582
I've already gotten used to this.

356
00:25:21,799 --> 00:25:23,438
Let's go somewhere else.

357
00:25:23,440 --> 00:25:26,580
Where can we go? It's crowded everywhere.

358
00:25:27,799 --> 00:25:31,440
I'm sure there's a place that is empty.

359
00:25:40,000 --> 00:25:44,960
   

360
00:25:50,120 --> 00:25:53,120
- You can go in now. 
 - Thank you. Okay.

361
00:25:58,759 --> 00:26:01,000
- Thank you, Sir. 
 - You may go in.

362
00:26:08,000 --> 00:26:11,459
It's so late now. Why did he allow us to come in?

363
00:26:11,459 --> 00:26:14,640
I told him that I was a student here.

364
00:26:14,640 --> 00:26:17,160
I wanted to show my school to my girlfriend.

365
00:26:17,160 --> 00:26:19,437
He said he still remembered me.

366
00:26:19,437 --> 00:26:22,740
Scholar-God Yu Tu. Of course, he remembers.

367
00:26:23,503 --> 00:26:27,279
Unfortunately, it's not convenient for my girlfriend to show her face.

368
00:26:27,279 --> 00:26:30,219
Otherwise, we could enter the school even more easily.

369
00:26:30,219 --> 00:26:31,819
You're right.

370
00:26:35,319 --> 00:26:39,000
In fact, I was here in the morning. He didn't notice me.

371
00:26:39,880 --> 00:26:41,950
Were you here this morning?

372
00:26:56,580 --> 00:26:59,037
What happened to the field?

373
00:26:59,039 --> 00:27:01,198
I guess they are expanding.

374
00:27:01,198 --> 00:27:02,880
Oh, yes.

375
00:27:02,880 --> 00:27:07,179
Did you once pick flowers with some other female students

376
00:27:07,179 --> 00:27:09,303
and got reprimanded by our class teacher?

377
00:27:10,759 --> 00:27:13,772
Can't you remember something good about me?

378
00:27:18,699 --> 00:27:20,199
Let's go.

379
00:27:41,799 --> 00:27:43,640
Back then, after I finished eating at the canteen.

380
00:27:43,640 --> 00:27:45,720
I would take this way to go back to the classroom.

381
00:27:45,720 --> 00:27:48,240
At that time, I thought our school was the most beautiful place.

382
00:27:48,240 --> 00:27:50,317
I think you rarely came here.

383
00:27:50,319 --> 00:27:51,918
I was usually at the field,

384
00:27:51,918 --> 00:27:53,878
so I seldom ran into you.

385
00:27:53,880 --> 00:27:56,398
Once, I ran into you...

386
00:27:56,398 --> 00:27:57,759
There.

387
00:27:57,759 --> 00:27:59,759
Do you remember that incident?

388
00:28:07,880 --> 00:28:09,840
 Yu Tu, are you free? 

389
00:28:09,840 --> 00:28:11,797
 I have a question for you. 

390
00:28:11,799 --> 00:28:13,760
 Sure. Go ahead. 

391
00:28:15,179 --> 00:28:17,040
 Yu Tu, do you not have a girlfriend right now? 

392
00:28:17,040 --> 00:28:20,300
 If so, what do you think of me? 

393
00:28:25,519 --> 00:28:27,119
When we were on our way,

394
00:28:27,119 --> 00:28:29,240
I was thinking about something.

395
00:28:29,240 --> 00:28:30,940
What is it?

396
00:28:34,559 --> 00:28:36,905
What should I do if you bring up the past?

397
00:28:38,559 --> 00:28:40,640
Not today.

398
00:28:43,728 --> 00:28:45,828
But I might in the future.

399
00:28:54,000 --> 00:28:55,794
I'm looking forward to it.

400
00:29:28,160 --> 00:29:29,660
We've arrived.

401
00:29:35,620 --> 00:29:37,491
I can't see anything.

402
00:29:44,359 --> 00:29:47,259
Look. They have changed all the desks and chairs.

403
00:29:48,119 --> 00:29:51,479
That's for sure. It's been more than ten years.

404
00:29:51,479 --> 00:29:53,799
Your seat was in the last row.

405
00:29:54,839 --> 00:29:57,180
Do you remember where my seat was?

406
00:29:58,480 --> 00:30:00,180
In the third row.

407
00:30:01,839 --> 00:30:04,860
Do you remember everyone's seats?

408
00:30:04,860 --> 00:30:09,140
I don't believe you cared about where I sat.

409
00:30:09,140 --> 00:30:13,680
Lately, I've been trying to recall what happened in high school.

410
00:30:16,400 --> 00:30:18,441
Then what have you recalled?

411
00:30:19,480 --> 00:30:23,740
I recalled how you bribed me with fried chicken to teach you math.

412
00:30:23,740 --> 00:30:25,820
Why do you only recall the bad things?

413
00:30:25,820 --> 00:30:28,119
I can bring up the past too.

414
00:30:35,559 --> 00:30:39,400
At that time, I had a goal

415
00:30:39,400 --> 00:30:41,779
that I failed to achieve.

416
00:30:44,359 --> 00:30:46,559
You wanted to go to the same university as me.

417
00:30:48,680 --> 00:30:50,280
How do you know?

418
00:30:51,019 --> 00:30:55,560
I read the conversation in the Space Fans chatroom.

419
00:30:55,560 --> 00:30:57,993
You even found the chatroom.

420
00:31:01,160 --> 00:31:03,600
I believe that you've really been trying to recall everything.

421
00:31:07,620 --> 00:31:11,459
In fact, I was pretty depressed during that time.

422
00:31:11,459 --> 00:31:14,040
I got good grades in junior high school.

423
00:31:14,040 --> 00:31:16,318
I was very confident.

424
00:31:17,040 --> 00:31:19,378
But when I started high school,

425
00:31:19,378 --> 00:31:21,518
my results were not as good as before.

426
00:31:21,518 --> 00:31:24,987
I always thought that as long as I worked hard enough,

427
00:31:24,987 --> 00:31:27,567
I would get a better score.

428
00:31:28,759 --> 00:31:31,259
I only found out later

429
00:31:31,259 --> 00:31:36,240
