430
00:31:41,200 --> 00:31:43,007
I should have taught you.

431
00:31:47,880 --> 00:31:49,808
Would you have the patience?

432
00:31:50,599 --> 00:31:52,199
I would.

433
00:31:53,739 --> 00:31:57,079
What if I had been really stupid and understood nothing?

434
00:31:58,180 --> 00:32:00,060
You would have understood it well

435
00:32:00,760 --> 00:32:03,117
